//Food and Drink Java Beach, 1396 La Playa St, San Francisco, CA 94122 Good spot to grab a coffee before checking Ocean Beach. 849VQF6R+5CM Pittsburgh’s Pub, 4207 Judah St, San Francisco, CA 94122 Divey, divey bar. 849VQF6V+34F Beachside Cafe, 4542 Irving St, San Francisco, CA 94122 Good post-surf brunch spot. 849VQF6R+5MH Celia\'s, 4019 Judah St, San Francisco, CA 94122 Can\'t go wrong with Taco Tuesday\'s here. 849VQF6V+4W9 Trouble Coffee, 4033 Judah St, San Francisco, CA 94122 Small coffee spot with a nice patio. 849VQF6V+4V Yonker\'s Cafe, 3815 Noriega St, San Francisco, CA 94122 Pre and post surf sandwiches. 849VQF3W+44 Pizza Place on Noriega, 3901 Noriega St, San Francisco, CA 94122 Laidback pizza place where you\'ll see a lot of familiar faces from the water. 849VQF3V+4Q Flanahan\'s Pub, 3805 Noriega St, San Francisco, CA 94122 Cash only pub where locals hang 849VQF3W+45 Riptide, 3639 Taraval, San Francisco, CA 94116 Burnt down a few years ago, but back with vengeance. 849VPFRV+MV White Cap, 3608 Taraval St, San Francisco, CA 94116 Owned and operated by surfers. 849VPFRW+Q2 Andytown, 3655 Lawton St, San Francisco, CA 94122 Try a snowy plover. Thank us later. 849VQF4X+M3
//Events Outside Lands, Golden Gate Park If you have money check out this giant music festival in Golden Gate Park featuring all the latest chart toppers. Held early August. 849VQG97+QG Hardly Strictly Bluegrass, Golden Gate Park Outside Lands freer, quirker, lessy poppy older brother. Check out this free sprawling music festival in early October. 849VQG97+QG Stern Grove Music Festival, Stern Grove Free Sunday concerts featuring a wide range of artists and genres all summer long. 849VPGMF+XP Noriega Street Fair, Outer Sunset, San Francisco Small, fun neighborhood street fair held in October. 849VQF3W+64
